{"about_the_game":"<br><br>Welcome to the Retro Drive universe - a haven where the spirit of the 80s blazes with neon brilliance. Dash into a time-traveling vortex of neon lights and pulsating beats.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142380/extras/RDR_Mechanics.gif?t=1726511295\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142380/extras/SteamBanners_RetroRacer_En.png?t=1726511295\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">WELCOME TO RETROPOLIS</h2>Conquer the vibrant streets of Retropolis. Whether it's racing against the clock or evading the police, your skills will be put to the test. Turn the volume up, put the pedal to the metal, and race to catch up with your pals!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142380/extras/RDR_Racing_0.4.gif?t=1726511295\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142380/extras/SteamBanners_RideInStyle_En.png?t=1726511295\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">RADICAL CARS</h2>Build up your points as you race to unlock an array of customisable cars. The cooler your ride, the faster you'll tear through Retropolis. Cruise the neon-lit streets in style!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142380/extras/RDR_Racing_0.5.gif?t=1726511295\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2142380/extras/SteamBanners_RadSoundtrack_En.png?t=1726511295\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">SYNTHWAVE LEGENDS</h2>Immerse yourself in the synthwave universe with an unforgettable soundtrack featuring artists like:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>New Arcades<br></li><li>Neon Nox<br></li><li>Fantom '87<br></li><li>Michael Oakley<br></li><li>Sunglasses Kid<br></li><li>and many more</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https